record.title: MEASURES PLACED ON THE CALENDAR--S. 1301 AND S. 1305

speaking.paragraph: It is my understanding there are two bills at the desk due for a second reading.

record.chair: Without objection, the clerk will report.
record.narrative: The legislative clerk read as follows:

speaking.paragraph: I object to any further proceedings with respect to these bills en bloc.

record.chair: Objection is heard. The bills will be placed on the calendar.
